Winning numbers drawn in ‘Georgia FIVE Midday’ game
ATLANTA (AP) _ The winning numbers in Thursday afternoon’s drawing of the Georgia Lottery’s “Georgia FIVE Midday” game were:
9-8-6-3-7
(nine, eight, six, three, seven)
